name: Racheal Collins
description:
Well More importantly.I love spending time with those around me that mean the most I love to meet new people and see new places. I’m a very sweet, very flirty. I’m honest, caring, loyal, trusting, loving. I enjoy the small things in life and I don’t take them for granted.
I’m looking for some good, solid people to connect with for good times and lots of laughs. I’m looking for the type of guy with good personality, sence of humor, trusting, honest,caring, loving,fun to be around with, I want someone who actually knows what he wants and knows what the other wants and respects that.
